                work I can find! Honestly, I believe storytelling has been a part of me for as long as I can remember. 
                Over the years, I’ve developed countless unique universes and narratives, each one helping me grow and refine my skills. 
                That journey has led me to my current focus: developing The Packs and Grounded—two original 
                projects that I’m deeply passionate about and actively working on as I write this
                Most of those earlier projects were developed using an animatic, 
