        <h1>Team Management</h1>
    </div>
        <p>
                I have led multiple animation teams of 10 to 30 members on projects such as 
                THE PACKS, Let’s Try Again, and GROUNDED Episodes 1 and 2. 
                I formed and managed a production-focused Discord group, 
